title: Ebro In The Morning - Panama Papers + Wale Appreciation
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 10/4. 

Ebro and the crew talk about Wale because of his new hit-single with J. Cole "Poke It Out" and the Panama Papers. Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments at minutes 12, 40, & 1:07.
